            "answer_text": "To \u201cWalk the Line\u201d in a relationship basically means to do exactly what you should do when in a relationship. This is also exactly what you would want your husband/ wife, boyfriend/ girlfriend to do. To be true., Not to get into a situation that might have you fall into temptation. \u201cI keep a close watch on this heart of mine, I keep my eyes wide open all the time, because your mine, I walk the line.\u201dYou keep your emotions in check, and your eyes open, not letting them stray, or having eyes for someone else. This phrase was more common prior to the late 60\u2019s. \u201cBecause your mine, I walk the line.\u201d Translates to, Your the best thing that has happened to me, and I wouldn\u2019t do a thing to ruin our relationship. I hope this helps. ",
